      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-sad-dat-sad        to   s-dat                  .
           add       1                    to   s-gio                  .
           move      "CD"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
